channel.title: 562 loading 602 failing to start
channel.description:
Hello.
I have been trying to get my 562 loading 602 to start, but I can't and I have been trying FOR 3 DAYS to find a solution.
The best I have had so far, using different "602 caches" is "Loading updates - 3%". After this, it says "error-js5-connect" and freezes. I'm also using Khanz's 562 IP changer client.
Please aid me out if you can, thanks! I think it might have something to do with my cache but I dunno.
